EMAIL & MULTI-CHANNEL EXPERIMENTS
ONBOARDING EMAILS
Test Hypothesis Founder welcome email Personal vs. generic Behavior-based triggers Action/inaction based Email timing Immediate vs. delayed Email frequency More vs. fewer touches Quick tips format Short actionable content Video in email More engaging format 
EMAIL CONTENT
Test Hypothesis Subject lines Open rate optimization Personalization depth Name vs. behavior-based CTA prominence Single clear action Social proof inclusion Testimonials in email Urgency messaging Trial reminders Plain text vs. designed Format testing 
FEEDBACK LOOPS
Test Hypothesis NPS during onboarding WT ask Blocking question "What's stopping you?" NPS follow-up Actions based on score In-app feedback Thumbs up/down on features Survey timing WT request feedback Feedback incentives Reward for completing 
