RE-ENGAGEMENT EXPERIMENTS
STALLED USER RECOVERY
Test Hypothesis Re-engagement email timing WT send Personal outreach Human vs. automated Simplified path Reduced steps for returners Incentive offers Discount or extended trial Problem identification Ask what's blocking Demo offer Live walkthrough 
RETURN EXPERIENCE
Test Hypothesis Welcome back message Acknowledge return Progress resume Pick up where left off Changed state What happened while away Re-onboarding Fresh start option Urgency messaging Trial time remaining 
